xt":"Beautiful property. Delicious food. Comfortable with sophisticated ambiance. Separate his & hers showers. Very spacious with a pool. Service was phenomenal! Recommended.","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"Monica Van Lucien","rating":5,"text":"10/10\n\nVisited here as a non-resident as I was touring Greece, Aman is truly worth it, doesn''t compete with any other resorts, I must say the hospitality is truly exceptional this is one of the most extraordinary experiences I have received in Greece to date!","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"Walker Duncan","rating":5,"text":"10/10! Hope to visit other Amans one day as the Amanzoe was excellent in every way. Thanks for taking care of all of us - the wedding we attended there was handled wonderfully and beautifully from start to finish. Thanks to all the staff members who worked tirelessly with nothing but smiles.","time":"4 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
