relaxation. The service felt so personal and genuine, which made our stay even more special.\n\nA huge thank you to the amazing teams at reception, the restaurant, bar, spa, and housekeeping for making our time at Acro Suites unforgettable. You all went above and beyond to make our stay perfect.\n\nWe are already looking forward to returning - Acro Suites truly sets the standard for exceptional hospitality!","time":"2 months ago"},{"author":"Scott McDonald","rating":4,"text":"Bills itself as 5 star and Michelin Rated. Stay was okay. It was our least favorite SLH and hotel stay during our few week visit to Greece.\n\nStaff was pleasant. However never chatty and seemed like they didn‚Äôt want to be there.\n\nPool was always too cold to use.\n\nHotel is very far away from anything. So only stay here if you do not want to leave the resort.\n\nDrying clean laundry on dusty rocks was disturbing. Reading lights flashed. Frayed wires on lights. Rust on the pool. Trash and missing vent covers.\n\nAttached to another resort that had constant flows of your buses. Also the visitors there kept trying to get into the gym and other areas of Acro suites.\n\nWe honestly just expected more. Sunrises were nice. But after staying 5 nights we saw behind the curtains a little more.\n\nAfter coming from Canaves Epitome in Santorini. This stay just left us wanting a lot more. Would never come back to stay here again.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Nick Stachel","rating":5,"text":"My wife and I spent the first few days of our honeymoon at Acro Suites and couldn‚Äôt have asked for a better start. We were welcomed warmly, the staff was attentive, and the food was outstanding. They made us feel truly cared for, and we‚Äôll be recommending this place to everyone we know.\n\nA special shoutout to Antonis, Andres, and Zacharais for making it a great and  memorable stay for us!","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Mark Verheyen","rating":5,"text":"This hotel can be described with one word: WOW!\nThere is simply not a negative thing to mention. The rooms are really spacious, beautiful and well designed. The personnel is so sweet, they treat you like a king (and queen). And the location on the cliffs it''s just so stunning!\nWould recommend 10/10.","time":"2 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
