g from abroad! Masia Cabellut lived up to‚Äîand surpassed‚Äîall of our expectations. The aesthetic, the seamless blend of old and new, the views, and the delicious wines (we loved them all!) cannot be beat.\n\nWe stayed on-site with our family and a few friends, and the accommodations were absolutely breathtaking. Every inch of Masia Cabellut has been renovated with such intention and care. Our wedding day itself is one that our guests will never forget‚Äîtruly the most stunning venue any of us have ever seen.\n\nBeyond the beauty, every member of the staff was incredibly warm, helpful, and professional. They are truly a top-of-the-line team. We can‚Äôt wait to return in the future and will cherish our memories at Masia Cabellut for a lifetime!","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Jessica Abobo","rating":5,"text":"Absolutely jaw dropping in so many ways!\n\nWe dreamt of a venue that was a vineyard and Masia Cabellut checked off all the boxes. We booked for our destination wedding this past June back in 2023 sight unseen. The property from the vineyard, gardens, to the house - gorgeous and thoughtfully laid out and planned.\n\nWe book three days and had wished we had more time. All of the staff from booking to our stay were so responsive, attentive, and just so helpful.\n\nOur wedding day was a dream. Everything we could have imagined plus more. The setting made it dreamy, romantic, and whisical. Definitely memories we will cherish for a lifetime.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Luting Chen","rating":5,"text":"We only happened to visit one wedding venue and decided to go with Masia Cabellut immediately after the visit. Rob and Jurate were incredibly helpful and responsive. We loved our wedding there!","time":"in the last week"},{"author":"Lauren Haynes","rating":5,"text":"We had the most incredible experience at Masia Cabellut for our April 2025 wedding. From the early planning stages to day-of execution, everyone we communicated with was kind and professional. They made planning easy, and were very accommodating in helping our \"vision\" come to life. The grounds were perfectly maintained, and the staff (especially Rob) were great about checking in with us the days leading up to the wedding.\n\nWe have received countless compliments from guests regarding the beauty of Masia Cabellut. Everywhere you looked was perfect and picturesque. And the wine - incredible! This place will always have a special place in our hearts, and for that we are incredibly grateful.","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"Nathan Agland","rating":5,"text":"Wow! Masia Cabellut is without a doubt one of the most incredible properties we''ve ever experienced. From the moment we arrived, we were blown away by the stunning surroundings - acres of beautiful nature, vineyards and rich history that made the whole place feel like something out of a dream.\n\nThe property itself is immaculate with every design and detail thoughtfully curated to make the stay feel effortlessly perfect. But what truly made our experience unforgettable was the people. A huge and heartfelt thank you to Jurate and Roberto in particular who went above and beyond (again and again and again!) Your warmth, professionalism, and care made all the difference. We couldn‚Äôt have asked for a more magical setting or better team to help us celebrate our big day. Highly, highly recommended.","time":"9 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
