er worked at. Just 25 minutes from Barcelona, it offers a perfect mix of elegance, history, and nature.\n\nThe castle itself is majestic, with incredible architecture, grand staircases, and impressive statues spread throughout the grounds. The landscaped gardens are lush and peaceful ‚Äî a dream setting for both ceremony and celebration.\n\nOne of our favorite details is the open-air banquet setup, where guests dine under the stars surrounded by floral installations. The florist team did a beautiful job preparing the tables, from the bride and groom‚Äôs sweetheart table to every small detail of the centerpieces.\n\nWe captured the wedding cake reveal in the disco hall, a powerful and cinematic moment, and finished with drone shots that show the full beauty of the venue from above.\n\nFor anyone dreaming of a truly magical wedding in Spain, this castle delivers unforgettable memories.","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"Shailendra Chopra","rating":5,"text":"Attended a wedding there.\nA little bit of a drive, but the grounds are fabulous. June was hot so dress accordingly. The experience was magical!","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"Sanjay Subhedar","rating":5,"text":"Visited for a wedding. Beautiful gardens and nice salon for cocktails and dancing. Very popular site for weddings and events","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Jackie Chick","rating":5,"text":"Castell Sant Mar√ßal is one of those places that really sparks creativity as a photographer. I was part of a photography team here, and from the moment I arrived, I knew it was going to be special. The variety of photo spots is incredible‚Äîwhether it‚Äôs the elegant interiors or the scenic outdoor spaces, there‚Äôs always something unique to capture. For me, it‚Äôs all about creating artistic, unconventional images, and this venue made that effortless.\n\nThe staff were super friendly and helpful, which added to the experience. If you‚Äôre a couple looking for a venue that offers endless photographic possibilities, Castell Sant Mar√ßal is the place. You‚Äôll love how versatile and beautiful the venue is. I‚Äôm definitely looking forward to the chance to shoot here again!","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"James Hashim","rating":4,"text":"This is a beautiful wedding venue. A real Spanish castle.","time":"5 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
