 wealth of experience was invaluable, and she went above and beyond to ensure everything was flawless‚Äînot just for the wedding itself but also for additional arrangements like organizing the AV and transportation for our guests.\n\nThe staff were absolutely wonderful, so friendly and attentive throughout the event. And the food‚Äîwow! Everyone is still talking about how delicious it was. Finca Mas Solers provided an unforgettable experience, and we would highly recommend it to anyone looking for a stunning venue with a fantastic team.\n\nP.S. The photos online don''t do this venue justice - highly recommend going to see it for yourself. It will take your breath away.","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"Mariana Serrano","rating":5,"text":"Great event house with spacious salons and good lighting. Surrounded by trees, this is a very calm space for great events.","time":"3 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
