iquel Salas</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"Brett Williams","rating":4,"text":"Popped in for menu of the day which was great value , food wasn‚Äôt the best but as this was a fixed menu for just ¬£15 or so which came with wine and desert , i cant be too critical. Rice had an unusual ras el hanout flavour which wasn‚Äôt expected. Great service and locally owned so will be back to try the main menu.","time":"2 years ago"},{"author":"Littlejar Littlejar","rating":5,"text":"This place is really really good and worth. The owner Toni is a wonderful person always taking care of the customer''s needs. Never had a problem with my allergy,  they adapt all the dishes for me. It''s value for money!!! Food is lavish.","time":"3 years ago"},{"author":"Brian Cleave","rating":5,"text":"We are not strangers to Sa Fortaleza but we haven''t been for a while.  For a small bar restaurant we had a superb meal. The  ceasar salad starter was amazing. The ingredients gave us a huge range of taste and a lot on the plate. I had their pork loin in an apple sauce with delicious chips. I meant to ask if they were air fried because they were so good. All this, plus a delicious Rueda white wine served very cold. Toni, you and your family do us proud. Gracias","time":"2 years ago"},{"author":"Lorenza Zorer","rating":5,"text":"We were  looking for restaurants that were open and would have traditional food. I saw this place on google, we quickly booked a table. We sat outside, the stuff was super kind and friendly. We ordered 2 starters but we got some other starters offered. They all were absolutely amazing, from traditional grilled squid to croquetas with mushroom (that you literally will want more from) to octopus. For main dish we had cod fish which was also very good. I have to say, I am always a bit picky with food, I do like to cook myself so I have high standarts when I go for dinner somewhere and this place is a true joy to go to! Not only for the awesome food but also the atmosphere and owner.","time":"4 years ago"},{"author":"Eddie Burne","rating":5,"text":"Really good food went with a group of 30 people pre booked was great meal. Wine l√±cluded 22euros per head. Service.good parking easy and free. Good night out. Drink prices cheap.","time":"7 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
