g-qyw6psxM_emOwILEYPgA","width":1920,"height":1204,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/103196732268327974817\">Castell Son Claret - Leading Hotels of the World Mallorca</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN2jabL-goLL1lMdczzJbERPyFcIfBr8TvH40KMtpv1bUw7KlEoFPAkxKP8KFmlg17y87qhuaRoRGli5yAaTao0LOvB_gKYiQ1eMjYGvgMUQpX1NgaDp0pdMxa2G37wpVKuQWwqSaR0Iv1TA8tuMh3V38UlnJjPZ0ktbjGDufMK3iNZ68GQ_E0kj8tA0eE9UvmhRn6liWGEMMKC0ZvSBoHPqSCyU6zQK0iFmxbcjXtbjp8PXSIJ2ovZemlwtUBRpiTGxl-5sawz3ceUiFLQLTt789K0pEwSyXfhvqGtjqggQMw","width":4296,"height":2864,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/103196732268327974817\">Castell Son Claret - Leading Hotels of the World Mallorca</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN0wP0s9Jnj9Nv9ZUfC2UkW7T6FmqqstQ53lhkxuP1ZG2HxhGNUt54Ve0J5y8xpn4zinBwb79rr_R7In3TpB0znAaHqZLaaNWp6I34cciVHP8ipiofajqTGWVxV0m4LPj0r1YOEU1Gq3VizqYrfV0aPg_yk0djE0itOMkLO4QAu253OsoQyx-MGpS4f0nsmRnDpkY-U9fPotKqBz7Iec3rv5JuPquWRSntyLag_r1h8DRrZ0i0Bwu0hvJ0M3INqzxJKYu606_kTc4f6h8csD4bjlzdJ3FOGdYusVmcrKjVO6ZQ","width":4800,"height":3201,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/103196732268327974817\">Castell Son Claret - Leading Hotels of the World Mallorca</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"Jennifer L","rating":5,"text":"We had a wonderful stay at Castell Son Claret. After coming from a lively beach resort, the peacefulness of this property were a welcome change. The gardens are truly stunning, and the service throughout our stay was warm and attentive.\n\nOur room interiors looked a bit dated, but they were still very well maintained-spacious, clean, and comfortable. The bedding was wonderful!  Breakfast was a real highlight for me, and we also loved our poolside afternoons and relaxed dinners on-site.\n\nLovely place and would recommend!","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"Rainer-Christian Koppitz","rating":5,"text":"Beautiful, luxury hide-away in a very quiet, green valley in the Tramuntana mountains. Far away from the noise and crowds elsewhere on Mallorca.\nPerfect, extremely friendly service, excellent food and wines, fantastic pool and a lot of nature.\nSummary: If you need some quiet time in a wonderful surrounding - that''s the place to go on Mallorca.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Lauren Newman","rating":2,"text":"The estate and grounds are absolutely beautiful. But the service is atrocious. In no means is this a five star hotel. If it was four stars and less expensive it would‚Äôve made sense. However it was not. Upon checking in they were unprepared and it was bad service from the start. They offered us free breakfast since our room wasn‚Äôt ready, and then retracted the offer once we were eating, making us pay. They didn‚Äôt notify us when the room was ready as promised, so we waited at the pool in the rain for two extra hours. Upon checking in we wanted to shower and nap. However the shower was broken, spewing water all over the entire bathroom. And the bed sheets were stained with what looked like blood. They came to fix that all but no apologies. There was no valet ready to attend to your car, despite being told you can only valet (we often had to walk inside to hand them the keys, and sometimes no one was even there). There‚Äôs a small staff and they‚Äôre rarely around. No water in the room with daily cleaning service, no turn down service. If you are expecting five star service at this ‚Äúfive star‚Äù hotel, definitely go elsewhere, as you won‚Äôt find it here. If you want to overpay for a pretty castle with bad service, you‚Äôve found the place. (After checking out they charged us for meals and drinks we never got‚Ä¶ and refused to take them off the bill)","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Joshua Church","rating":5,"text":"4th year going to Castell and will be going again next year.\n\nRoberto and Jacob on the bar never fail to impress, Stephanie and Pablo and Auriel on the pool bar just so friendly and attentive and Eduardo and another character (I didn''t catch the name of) on the breakfasts making us feel really welcome. We had a slight issue the first night and it was fixed very quickly and they constantly made our 16 month old feel very welcome.\n\nSee you next year.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Nour Kubursi","rating":5,"text":"We had an incredible stay here for our honeymoon. This hotel is everything you could ask for during your stay in Mallorca. Great staff, excellent food and clean and cozy rooms. Highly recommend!!!!","time":"3 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
