 after dinner.","time":"2 months ago"},{"author":"Sergio Sovero","rating":1,"text":"Absolutely unacceptable experience ‚Äî stay away.\n\nTo make the story short, two cockroaches were found in the bathroom during my stay. I immediately called the front desk expecting urgency or at least some level of concern. Instead, a staff member casually came to the room, killed one of the cockroaches, couldn‚Äôt find the other one, and just left as if this was completely normal. No apology, no shock, nothing.\n\nI asked to be moved to a different room ‚Äî a very reasonable request ‚Äî and was told it was ‚Äúnot possible,‚Äù even though the hotel was clearly not sold out. I ended up barely sleeping all night knowing there was still a cockroach loose somewhere in the room. Completely unacceptable, unsanitary, and unprofessional.\n\nI‚Äôm attaching videos and photos because this experience speaks for itself. This property needs serious attention to cleanliness and customer service. I will not be returning and cannot recommend it to anyone.\n\nSo far, I emailed the GM a week ago and no reply! They simply don‚Äôt care. Good luck staying in this ‚Äúluxury collection‚Äù property.\n\nRegards,\nA Marriot Platinum Elite Member","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"David McMurtrie","rating":5,"text":"Beautiful hotel situated in the hills above Palma and with great views over the city. Conveniently situated for three world class golf courses but you don''t need to play golf to enjoy staying here.\nThe hotel has a lovely pool and the restaurants are excellent.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"David Grantham","rating":5,"text":"This is by far one of the best hotels I have ever stayed in. The staff is amazing! So friendly and extremely helpful with anything needed! The atmosphere is beautiful with such comfortable rooms!! Guaranteed to get a great night sleep. The food is over the top! You will not be disappointed at all!","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Blake Thornton","rating":5,"text":"Incredible hotel from start to finish. Gorgeous historic property with stunning views over Palma, spacious and comfortable rooms, and a peaceful pool area perfect for relaxing. Service was flawless and every staff member went above and beyond. Breakfast was outstanding every day. Easily one of the best luxury stays in Mallorca.","time":"5 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
