</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN2ndTB3Ewc8wKDDjrB60rTBQF18ia3k-zV2S1aC5SvrZmbPUUKNgWDAMEoM4wWGIS7L9ylrLFMNwDiWCegCrX5_jDfdFV4l4m1w6cwKXL_W2UN6U0Rshw2KDChK1iWMWfRxAEv4-V9ijHYrA6eHIkgjKuEElwi-dMl7NaZENmv72KCzyI9lrWP8kOsOlwj9oexDIDqCVhs6LrBu7r4dG7ROYsA7B1O34QbVPZI3PVoltOJmVs3TqgLKPeopyWcZzRyHsAc4I8ebmgEjcvnlJo8wIUnJ4VDoE8kA8b2YWn2yPA","width":2880,"height":1920,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/108414275148514025056\">7Pines Resort Ibiza, a Destination by Hyatt Hotel</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN018Rws_HkeR8QUhNsj7P-TDW1j-2xTHWPVmrtE8GDdXEBj2IXfa_5JaPUQoKA9bgPV8QiIEEfZIbubS_DObf79a_cd9RRKqE3hyqtWrBq4iPidhKnnN4GgFcvTypPZ1yFFOTImNsvA6UwMKLtg8QOeHLcpZIAWZqZ5uKvCkL8Rqo_l-p2v1R_bXC2WUa8HRw1qCw7T15mmKQ9EypqFrrI9bTBwHp0q_STU5K8hwha1AwNbYZnO1nc2DOWKKBKJRAiSstrYX8bsVoi4N-fzFHGYQw5wK0NfE29ayxc4yMaYdA","width":2736,"height":1824,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/108414275148514025056\">7Pines Resort Ibiza, a Destination by Hyatt Hotel</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"Alessandro Malvitti","rating":5,"text":"We had a truly pleasant overnight stay at 7Pines Ibiza. The room was spacious, clean, and tastefully decorated, with all the amenities you would expect from a luxury resort. The bed was exceptionally comfortable, and the overall atmosphere of the property made it easy to relax and disconnect.\n\nBreakfast the next morning was excellent. There was a wide selection of high-quality items, both sweet and savory, and everything was beautifully presented. The pancakes stood out! Freshly made, soft, and perfectly balanced in flavor. Service was attentive but discreet, and the setting made the whole experience feel peaceful and refined.\n\nWe would definitely return.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"James Freel","rating":5,"text":"The stay overall was fantastic, but for us the highlight by far was the breakfast.\n\nOur breakfast at 7Pines was absolutely fantastic, and a huge part of that was due to Issachar. He provided first-class service from start to finish. He was incredibly personable and attentive, and nothing was too much trouble for him.\nIssachar, a big thank you from your \"amigos from Scotland\" for all your hard work and for making our breakfast experience so special!\n\nAnother big shout out to Enrique at the Cone Club chill out area for the sunset experience. We attended most evenings for food and drinks and again, his service was exceptional.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"M. Yoshi","rating":5,"text":"The location is absolutely stunning ‚Äì without question one of the best spots on the entire island. The staff are all very friendly and welcoming (every single one of them) and I want to give special recognition to Addaya from the pool bar, who took care of us throughout the day and made our experience unforgettable.\n\nThe DJ at the pool created the perfect vibe ‚Äì it honestly felt like living out my dream day, the kind I had only seen on YouTube videos of Ibiza beach clubs.\n\nLater at the sunset bar (Cone Club), the atmosphere was just as incredible. Roman made our night amazing with his attentive service and warm attitude.\n\nThank you, Addaya, Roman, the Cone Club team, and thank you, 7Pines.\n\nI will definitely come back, and this place has now become one of my go-to favorite locations in Ibiza.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Lucia Corral","rating":5,"text":"I celebrated my birthday with a romantic dinner at 7Pines Ibiza and it was truly unforgettable. The location is absolutely dreamy, with a breathtaking view that created the perfect atmosphere from the very beginning.\n\nEvery dish by Chef Bruno was a surprise and each course exceeded our expectations. What made the experience even more special was when Chef Bruno himself came out of the kitchen to introduce himself and personally ask how our dinner was going, a treatment worthy of a true luxury restaurant.\nEasily one of the best dinners we have ever had.\n\nI could not have asked for a better way to celebrate, and I have already decided that from now on, this is where I will celebrate all my birthdays.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Mayara Hiromi","rating":5,"text":"Amazing place! I would stay for many more days if I could, without a doubt.\nThe pool DJ is fantastic, and the whole atmosphere is super comfortable and relaxing.\nThe staff are very attentive and provide excellent service.\n\nA special thank-you to Addaya, who took care of us in the pool area for hours and was incredibly friendly.\nThank you so much for the wonderful service, Addaya‚Äîshe deserves a perfect 10 in every way!\n\nWe will definitely be back.\nThank you, 7Pines!","time":"3 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
