rves a special mention. Everything‚Äîfrom the music and the vibe to the attentive service‚Äîwas second to none. It really was perfect.\n\nThe crab croquettes were the absolute showstopper, highly recommend! The cocktails were also excellent, and honestly everything we tried was really good, but those croquettes‚Ä¶","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Lewis Jones","rating":5,"text":"Nikki Beach Ibiza is the definition of a perfect day out ‚Äî chic, lively, and full of great energy. The atmosphere is stunning, but what truly stood out was the incredible staff. From the moment we arrived, the service was absolutely flawless ‚Äî friendly, fast, and genuinely attentive. Nothing was too much trouble, and they made us feel like VIPs the entire day.\n\nYes, it‚Äôs on the expensive side, but it‚Äôs 100% worth it for the quality of the experience. The food and cocktails were excellent, the music set the perfect vibe, and everything ran smoothly thanks to the amazing team.\n\nIf you‚Äôre in Ibiza and want a luxury beach day with world-class service, this is the place. Highly recommend booking ahead.","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"Lovely Rose","rating":5,"text":"We had a wonderful experience here. 10/10 recommend! Great food, excellent service and vibes.\n\nI HIGHLY recommend having private pickup pre- arranged afterwards. Do not depend on taxis and uber. It took us 2 hours to get transportation back to our hotel.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Veronica Moreira Ribeiro","rating":5,"text":"What a great atmosphere, I‚Äôve been to quite a few beach clubs around the globe including Nikki beach MIAMI which is also awesome. But Nikki beach in Ibiza is another level. Friendly staff and amazing food, great Dj/ music and beautiful people.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Carly Burgess","rating":5,"text":"100% would recommend. Staff were incredibly attentive & professional.\nThe overall vibe was brilliant I would go back in a heart beat! Food was delicious and beautifully presented (specifically the guacamole). Drinks were also great. Just wish there was more beach!","time":"7 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
