staurant.\n\nWe arrived in the early hours when they had just opened, so there was plenty of free parking in front of the restaurant itself.\n\nThe beach is very nice, the sunbeds are very comfortable. The price of 160 euros for the two of us included the following things: sunbeds with umbrella, towels, water and sangria. The staff is very friendly, both on the beach and in the restaurant.\n\nWe ate sea bass in the restaurant, which was very tasty, and the view from the restaurant which is on the cliff is amazing.\n\nAlso, a table in the restaurant should be reserved in advance.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Christian Crostelli","rating":5,"text":"Stunning Dining Experience\nDelicious food with breathtaking views from a beautiful terrace. The place is very well managed, offering impeccable service and a stylish Swedish inspired design. Prices are mid-to-high range, but absolutely justified by the quality of the food and the overall experience","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"Waleed Bin Mohammed","rating":4,"text":"Very good view from here. The food was good as well.\n\nService was good from Miss. Chiara,\n\nGood verity as well. Some orders was not available but the replacement was quite enough to make it.","time":"7 months ago"},{"author":"Mehry Kioumarsi","rating":4,"text":"Quite a nice place, with friendly service, good food and ocean views. While I think we had the absolute best views of the dining area, we also were on the only spot with no fans/AC and it was quite hot. We went for my partner‚Äôs birthday, which I communicated to the service, so they brought us a beautiful dessert and sang happy birthday for him. When we asked for the bill, I saw that we were being charged for the dessert. I didn‚Äôt feel comfortable bringing it up as the meal had been quite pleasant and I didn‚Äôt want it to come across the wrong way as restaurants are not obliged to offer free items for celebrations, but would have loved to be able to choose myself from the dessert menu if I had known that beforehand - just an idea! Again, pretty great overall and would come again!","time":"9 months ago"},{"author":"Germanrubchinskiy","rating":2,"text":"Red Thai Curry - the curry was too watery.\n\nThe angus beef burger was ok. Beef was not of good quality and the burger bun was too hard.\n\nThe tiramisu wasn''t my taste at all, but that may be because they have a completely different understanding of what tiramisu is.\n\nView ist beautiful.","time":"3 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
