v5x-dHKn-QFLWG3ptzgsjRohi_xlu_17Hx4Q_3RDN_vJpZlh9gaP5hUhCMam2liRzmX2Px4Vv13uwvKiTZ5-fABvtPt6_g","width":3500,"height":2333,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/116407124335516724745\">Marbella Club Hotel</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN1z1BvmzY0mwNJj3qqQMhWSpVletejcET3LnOq_B3fxEJILabS3Cwfonm-95u-MIm9IYfOJbwaPVXlS8W8JBvKZ6VFNwbBnQHv5HArBK-7srouSX7qk2gxXZ--L_EpeohRKY8gd8GHelv_4ZIUJ3371CMNZMyiSWIS_Cbbi0a9hDTsCQZaXFjH8WG2dun_jB78gfp6gOXy9h2MlVQJqeGDLgJRhJO2utfCjayG8ZUyC2vUlOSHhr3OwHpKwVYeOkwJIELg-Nk3_A52DG6kza9Xs0UaFcoq52TfNzsA4LUBp1A","width":1600,"height":2400,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/116407124335516724745\">Marbella Club Hotel</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"mark zeng","rating":5,"text":"Marbella Club excels in every aspect, offering an unparalleled experience of elegance and comfort.\n\nSpecial thanks to Maria and Jaden at the front desk for their exceptional professionalism and heartfelt hospitality ‚Äî they made our stay truly unforgettable.\n\nThe breakfast was remarkably generous and beautifully curated, easily one of the best among five-star hotels. The setting was equally elegant, making every morning feel like a serene indulgence.\n\nDinner was slightly on the pricier side, but the flavors were genuinely enjoyable and well-executed.","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"Mar√≠a Agustina","rating":5,"text":"The service is very good ‚Äî everyone is extremely attentive all the time. However, the room was quite outdated for what you would expect from a hotel of this category. The furniture looks old and very worn, and the d√©cor is rather unattractive.\nThe food offered through room service leaves a lot to be desired, especially considering the prices. A Caesar salad costs almost ‚Ç¨40, and there‚Äôs really nothing special about it ‚Äî I‚Äôd even dare to say the one from McDonald‚Äôs tastes better.\nOn the positive side, the Kids Club is absolutely beautiful and very well equipped. All the girls and boys who work there are truly professional and incredibly kind and loving with the children ‚Äî they do an excellent job.\nThe surroundings are beautiful and picturesque, and there‚Äôs always something going on in the evenings. The staff is VERY friendly, and there are plenty of services available. But honestly, I wouldn‚Äôt return, as the value for money just isn‚Äôt worth it.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"amina houssa","rating":1,"text":"Terrible service and security  very disappointing stay\nI stayed at Marbella Club Hotel for 4 days in room 266. During our stay, someone stole ‚Ç¨400 from my bag inside the room, and my friend also had $600 and ¬£100 stolen. We immediately reported it, but the staff did absolutely nothing. No apology, no investigation, no support just silence.\n\nThe service overall was terrible. Room service took over 2 hours to deliver food, and when it finally arrived, it was cold and poorly prepared.\n\nFor a hotel with this reputation, I expected much better. But instead, we felt unsafe, disrespected, and completely ignored. I do not recommend this place to anyone. The lack of security and basic service is unacceptable.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Gina Sayed","rating":5,"text":"This feels like a dreamresort and the best we ever visited. Everything is so well-mainted, clean and fresh smell. It was such a great pleasure to make a visit there. So many facilities like a wellness spa, kidsclub and you can walk straightaway into the beach and clear sea. Even the pool and bar is amazing. Beautiful location and awesome service from the staff, they so friendly and helpful. As a guest you truly feel welcome. This hotel even offers a few shops from famous brands.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Rub√©n ‚Äúrdouble‚Äù","rating":5,"text":"More Than a Stay ‚Äì A True State of Mind\n‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ\n\nMarbella Club isn‚Äôt just a hotel ‚Äî it‚Äôs a feeling. A rhythm. A completely different standard of luxury that you rarely find, even in the most prestigious places.\n\nFrom the moment we arrived, it was clear: this isn‚Äôt about flashy glamour. It‚Äôs understated elegance, deeply rooted in heritage and soul. The entire property is breathtakingly beautiful ‚Äî perfectly manicured gardens, timeless architecture, and a layout that feels more like a private village than a resort. Every corner has character. Every view is calming.\n\nOur suite was pure perfection ‚Äî spacious, refined, filled with natural light, and designed with a quiet sense of luxury that speaks for itself. Everything felt intentional, from the linens to the lighting.\n\nBut what truly sets Marbella Club apart is the service. This is not just staff ‚Äî these are hosts. Warm, intuitive, and effortlessly attentive without ever being intrusive. You don‚Äôt even need to ask ‚Äî they already know. Every interaction felt personal, not rehearsed.\n\nThere‚Äôs a serenity to this place that‚Äôs hard to describe. Whether you‚Äôre having breakfast under the bougainvillea, relaxing by the pool, or walking to the beach club ‚Äî you feel completely at ease.\n\nThis wasn‚Äôt a stay. This was a reset. We left feeling lighter, inspired, and already planning our return.\n\nMarbella Club doesn‚Äôt compete with other hotels ‚Äî it transcends them.","time":"5 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
