e, was a true gentleman and helped us arrange various events at the Cortijo including a bbq in the main courtyard and a Sunday Paella pool party the day after the wedding (which were both delicious!).\n\nWould definitely recommend booking this venue, particularly as a large group so you have exclusivity. But even as a single guest I am sure it would be great.","time":"6 years ago"},{"author":"Jeffrey Clark","rating":5,"text":"Great venue! We had a wonderful time at a wedding there. Really good service, good food, beautiful spaces!","time":"6 years ago"},{"author":"Nathaniel Francis","rating":5,"text":"We had our Wedding here run by Lucy & Jesus at Boutique Weddings Spain. The venue was INCREDIBLE on all accounts, friendly, accomodating, beautiful and stunning. The food was delicious and our planner was beyond amazing, patient, funny and on the ball to make sure everything was beyond perfect! Couldn''t recomend this venue or the planners enough! 100% worth it!","time":"8 years ago"},{"author":"Luis M AV","rating":5,"text":"It is surrounded by beautiful countryside, it''s near Seville (about 20 minutes). The pplace is okay, no disturbing, very relaxing.","time":"9 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
