 years ago"},{"author":"Salva de estamosgrabando","rating":5,"text":"In love","time":"4 years ago"},{"author":"Jag","rating":5,"text":"One of the best venues I''ve seen for weddings. It has different rooms, one for each part of the wedding. The banquet area is beautiful.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Isabella Girelli","rating":4,"text":"A beautiful location among olive groves and cypress trees, with plenty of space for the various wedding moments. We enjoyed the sunset at aperitif time. The lunch location, in the large courtyard of the \"Azienda\" (farm), was beautiful and evocative. It''s a shame about the \"Alvero\" (alverine) soil; us ladies, wearing sandals and heels, long dresses, and shawls, had a few moments of uncertainty. Afterward, we went to the disco area, with a bar and stage. Fun! Long live the newlyweds!","time":"3 years ago"},{"author":"Agustin","rating":5,"text":"I was recently at a dinner wedding. The Hacienda is beautiful. Since I was a guest, I''m only uploading a few photos I took without anyone being seen, but they capture the beauty of the venue. The large courtyard at the entrance to the complex, where we welcomed the bride and groom, is a truly spectacular space. And all surrounded by olive trees and nature.","time":"3 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
