rything was perfect, the place, the scenery, the service.  This venue has the perfect combination in between rustic and elegant at the same time.\nI have to say I was amazed by their customer service, I forgot a bag in the locker room area, they are closed on Mondays and I was returning back to my home country on Tuesday am.  I contacted them via DM on Instagram and they quickly responded, they made sure to get me in contact with the guard keeper.  He was so nice and helpful, and I was able to get my belongings right away even thought they were closed !  I even had cash in the bag and nothing was missing.  Thank you so much for your amazing service !!","time":"2 years ago"},{"author":"Nwanne Campo","rating":5,"text":"This is such an enchanting venue for classy events, I love it''s rustic yet elegant sceneries. I was there for Oto and Laura''s wedding on the 30th of June 2024, the staff were the best ever, so helpful, polite, nice and kind.","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"Gail Pilon","rating":5,"text":"This was the Wedding venue for our beautiful daughter-in-law & handsome son. It was beyond amazing. We could not have had a more fabulous property. Our Spanish & Canadian families & guests had a wonderful time. Muchas Gracias‚ù§Ô∏èüíõ‚ù§Ô∏èü§ç‚ù§Ô∏è","time":"10 months ago"},{"author":"Taylor c","rating":5,"text":"Planning a destination wedding from the United States could have been stressful, but choosing this venue in Spain was the best decision we made. From the very beginning, the coordinators were outstanding‚Äîprofessional, kind, responsive, and incredibly organized. They were in touch with us for many months leading up to the wedding, walking us through every detail and always making us feel heard and supported.\n\nWhat stood out the most was how effortlessly they brought everything together. The day of the wedding, I didn‚Äôt feel stressed at all‚Äîwhich says everything about the kind of team they are. They managed every detail behind the scenes with such grace and efficiency that we were able to fully relax and enjoy every moment.\n\nOur wedding day truly couldn‚Äôt have been more perfect. The setting was stunning, everything flowed beautifully, and the entire experience felt so personal and special. It was clear that they genuinely cared about making our day unforgettable.\n\nIf you''re considering this venue, don''t hesitate. You‚Äôll be working with a team of true professionals who are not only amazing at what they do, but who also put their heart into every step of the process.","time":"7 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
